  "title": "Cat Loaf (Bread Cats)",
  "description": "A literal cat loaf ᓚᘏᗢ - Cats now wear a fancy loaf of Bread",
  "body": "Have you ever wanted your Minecraft cats to be wearing loafs of bread?\nNo!?!?! Well you **should**!\n\nNow you can experience the joy of seeing Loafing Kitties all around your Minecraft world! ᓚᘏᗢ\n![Cats Loafing](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/NpAMtMuP/images/6a41f33a0d0e380c10af72da2ddd9562f89c3094.png)\n\n\n\n**Important:** This pack requires [EMF](https://modrinth.com/mod/entity-model-features) in order work, otherwise cats will just look like default.\n\nOfficially supports 1.21.11 and up! However it should work *mostly* fine in any version as far back as 1.20.2 (Kittens won't show up correctly in versions older than that since pack overlays didn't exist prior to that version)\n\nThis is my first time working with Java entity models, so I wouldn't be surprised if there was any issues I've missed. If you find any bugs then please let me know about them on my [discord server](https://discord.com/invite/HN2E9pVMK7) :)",
